
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>External CSS Example</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #2c3e50;
            text-align: center;
        }

        p {
            color: #555;
            font-size: 18px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>External CSS Implementation</h1>
    <p>Using external stylesheets improves reusability and consistency across multiple web pages.</p>
</body>
</html>





